---
title: Chipotle-Glazed Pork Chops with Garlic Mashed Potatoes and Roasted Broccoli
description: Pork, broccoli, and potatoes. Sounds pretty ordinary, right? Wrong! We’ve spiced up this classic dish with floral honey, a smoky chipotle glaze, and a touch of garlic. Get your taste buds ready; this dish packs an intense flavor punch that’ll have everyone begging for seconds.
